Cyberpunk style: A neon-drenched aerial view of a futuristic Singapore cityscape at night, with glowing fiber optic cables visibly threading through buildings like luminous blood vessels. Data streams represented as particles of cyan and magenta light race along these cables at varying speeds—some blazing fast, others crawling and stuttering. In the foreground, a frustrated figure sits at a floating holographic workstation, watching spinning loading indicators hover in mid-air while distant server towers pulse with energy across an ocean of dark water. The scene emphasizes the disconnect between raw bandwidth power and the maddening delay of distance, with visual "ping" ripples emanating outward toward faraway glowing horizons representing remote servers.
